com.tsgrp.migration.event

Class IntegerMultiplierListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.IntegerMultiplierListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener

    public class IntegerMultiplierListener
extends AbstractListener
implements TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener
    Problem- Source represents an interval of time as number of days, target uses number of years Solution- IntegerMultiplier This listener will take in an integer by which the value should be multiplied, and a String that will be the result if the result if the multiplication is invalid.
    Since:
    Oct 25, 2011

    Modification History

    • Oct 25, 2011 (Mike Sullivan) Created
